					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can use <a href="http://kkfos.aspekt.fi/projects/nes/tools/nintendulatordx/" class="postlink">NintendulatorDX</a> to figure out how many cycles a piece of code is taking. Simply write to $4020 when you want to start the timing and to $4030 when you want it to end. The README file has more info.</div>

					
